How to setup Atom for this project..

useful packages:
  ├── atom-beautify
  ├── atom-css-comb
  ├── atom-html-preview
  ├── color-picker
  ├── file-type-icons
  └── teletype

hint1:
  in index.html file --> to open web browser for realtime changes type:
    └── CTRL + SHIFT + H

hint2:
  setting up GitHub client in Atom:
    ├── on GitHub webpage: setting->developer settings->personal access tokens->generate token
    ├── in Atom: Packages->GitHub->Toggle GitHub Tab
    ├── copy token here
    ├── add project link: https://github.com/BrezinaAdam/GeneticAlgorithmVisualisation.git
    ├── first pull project
    ├── create your branch
    ├── make some changes
    ├── commit and push under your branch
    └── later merge with origin master

hint3:
  to make teletype work:
    ├── on GitHub webpage: setting->developer settings->personal access tokens->generate token
    ├── click teletype icon -> copy token here
    ├── join or generate portal ID
    └── collaborate with others on one file at one moment
